{"tid":1782512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[火上加油戰線] 就奧斯爾一事 幫全世界認識到大陸賤畜有幾賤","createTime":"2019-12-14T04:38:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T04:41:10.000Z","uid":273532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"94551f8ba3511de7d26ca30d63d341c726da0bbb","tid":1782512,"uid":273532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T04:38:20.000Z","msg":"目的：參考品葱「加速主義」嘅做法，周圍撥火，屌奧斯爾一個唔夠嘅，屌埋阿仙奴，令到全世界都見識到支那豬有幾咁大愛。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩法：<br />\n<br />\nStep 1 - 係ig同Twitter 申請個五毛fake account，改下啲on9名，例如: China man<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，加埋愛國icon就正啦<br />\n<br />\nStep 2 - like/retweet啲五毛言論<br />\n<br />\nStep 3 - 模仿五毛怒屌奧斯爾，要求阿仙奴炒咗佢，否則中國唔再播英超<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />， 呢啲你哋就自由發揮啦~ <br />\n<br />\nP.s. 如果唔識模仿五毛，可以直接copy佢哋嘅cm再加少少字眼就得，再唔係就用支那國旗洗版<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ffb1fdbc29f9c9b8c3d4d29fb42884b1e47ce5b","tid":1782512,"uid":251769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T04:41:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該推行動post</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pyqyGMZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpyqyGMZ.jpg&h=2f6dc79b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}